spec_data.Name: php-ezc-PersistentObjectDatabaseSchemaTiein
spec_data.Description:
The PersistentObjectDatabaseSchemaTiein component allows you to generate
template PersistentObject definition files and php classes from a database
structure or a DatabaseSchema schema file. You will most likely have to adjust
the PersistentObject definitions afterwards.
